creator: TRAINERIZE
descriptionHtml: Body Blueprint Fitness Coach is the last fitness app you'll ever need! We are not just a  fitness app, we are a personal training company based in Pennsylvania.  The first thing we do is assign you to a trainer and give you a direct line of communication to them!  The trainer will design a program to match your fitness goals.  So if you have a gym membership or have just your body weight to train with we got ya covered! With this fitness app, you can track your workouts and meals and we can visibly see the results (on screen and on you!).  Your personal trainer is available for any questions and to bust any plateaus.  Download the app today and see what results await you!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: First release of Body Blueprint Fitness Coach

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
As much as we’d all like, big changes unfortunately don’t happen overnight. That’s why we’ve introduced habit coaching—a new way to help clients make small, sustainable lifestyle changes! Trainers can now create habits within our Master Habit Library and prescribe them to clients. As clients complete habits each day, they will earn habit streaks and unlock special achievement badges over time.
As always, we’ve also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.
